1
00:00:01,760 --> 00:00:04,479
This is the 6198th year since the Demon Race descended
upon the Holy Demon Continent.

2
00:00:04,680 --> 00:00:07,079
The 6198th year
since the Demon Race descended
upon the Holy Demon Continent.

3
00:00:08,320 --> 00:00:10,279
After endless struggle,

4
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:11,999
and countless sacrifices,

5
00:00:13,440 --> 00:00:14,479
at this very moment,

6
00:00:15,840 --> 00:00:16,840
finally...

7
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:18,599
the Holy Demon Continent

8
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:21,519
has welcomed its own dawn.

9
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,999
The war between humans and demons

10
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,199
ends here.

11
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:27,359
Humanity

12
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,759
has claimed victory.

13
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:44,759
No wonder you managed to defeat
that old fool, the Demon God Emperor.

14
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:49,359
Becoming a god has made my dear brother much stronger indeed.

15
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,199
But if you think
that’s enough to beat me,

16
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,119
you’re still far from it.

17
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,040
By the laws of divinity,

18
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,479
this radiance ends here.

19
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,799
Not good enough, brother.

20
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,120
Your sword

21
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,599
is nothing but a child’s toy.

22
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,399
Once I destroy the Holy Demon Continent,

23
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,559
and obliterate the entire world,

24
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,079
only you and I will remain.

25
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,879
Because I dislike

26
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,999
anything superfluous.

27
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,600
Superfluous.

28
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,479
You actually managed to wound me.

29
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,639
Not bad at all, that strike.

30
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:09,999
Brother.

31
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,439
I’ve seen enough of ants building their nests.

32
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:24,919
Sorry about that,

33
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,920
brother.

34
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:27,599
I accidentally used a bit too much force.

35
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,480
I didn’t expect

36
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,439
that the so-called savior
of the Holy Demon Continent

37
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,199
would amount to so little.

38
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,439
If this is all you’re capable of,

39
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,839
then this needless affection of yours

40
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,199
is something you won’t be able to bear.

41
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,959
You had to test us first

42
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,199
before letting us come out.

43
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,200
You foolish child.

44
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,359
The old relic and the woman are here too.

45
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,360
Brother,

46
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,999
did you really think
adding them to your side

47
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,559
would change anything?

48
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,799
Why don’t we find out?

49
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,320
Let’s go!

50
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,799
The complete God of Heavenly Retribution

51
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,119
The complete God of Heavenly Retribution

52
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,199
is an existence that stands
above all other gods.

53
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,039
However, his power of Heavenly Retribution

54
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,040
is still sealed.

55
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,279
He is not in his complete form yet.

56
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,399
My divine power

57
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,439
can still harm him.

58
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,639
The three of us gods combined

59
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,000
are more than enough to face him.

60
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,960
Feng Xiu,

61
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,359
you pathetic stray dog.

62
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,239
How do you have the face

63
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,240
to stand before me?

64
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,839
Your manners have only gotten worse.

65
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,799
Austin Griffin,

66
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,599
after wandering for a thousand years,

67
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,559
you truly resemble a stray dog
of the void.

68
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,000
Woman,

69
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:16,039
what right do you have
to appear here?

70
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,399
Barking nonstop...

71
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:20,280
How noisy.

72
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,000
Brother,

73
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,159
relying on these old fossils
and a woman

74
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,319
is the only way you’ve lasted this long.

75
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,240
Aren’t you ashamed?

76
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,840
Are you jealous?

77
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,959
Then I’ll grant your wish.

78
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,919
Die together.

79
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,520
Did you think

80
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:49,919
I would come unprepared?

81
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,080
Did you think I would come unprepared?

82
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,839
Throne Law Seal

83
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:00,119
was set during our previous battle.

84
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,920
In three seconds,

85
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,999
everything will be destroyed.

86
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,839
Divine Seal Throne.

87
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:23,759
Origin Vortex.

88
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:24,760
Origin Vortex.

89
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,279
Myriad Phenomena Crucible.

90
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,080
What?

91
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,600
My technique...

92
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,000
has been deconstructed by you?

93
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,399
The Myriad Phenomena Crucible
can deconstruct all energy

94
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,439
and reshape it.

95
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,120
As long as I wish it,

96
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,639
your skills

97
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,079
will be unable to harm us.

98
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,120
Destruction

99
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,839
ends today.

100
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,400
Divine Realm.

101
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,519
Silent Light Shore.

102
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,520
Silent Light Shore.

103
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:17,999
In the name of the gods,

104
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,159
Dawn’s first light,
the twilight of the gods

105
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,639
descends upon this land.

106
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,879
Three gods working together...

107
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,719
Not bad at all.

108
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,919
Looks like I was played by you after all.

109
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,239
Brother.

110
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,160
Enough talk.

111
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,200
Now hand over your life!

112
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,000
Alright then.

113
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:58,600
I’ve had my fun.

114
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,800
Cai’er...

115
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,200
This aura...

116
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,799
It’s the true

117
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,199
God of Heavenly Retribution.

118
00:07:06,223 --> 00:07:29,023
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

119
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,959
Next,

120
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,439
let the world
pay homage

121
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:36,639
to the descent of the God of Heavenly Retribution.

122
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,279
You broke the seal.

123
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,959
My dear brother.

124
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,759
You all want to kill me.

125
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,639
If I don’t think of something,

126
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,159
should I just obediently wait for death?

127
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,759
That guy Chuangshi has been dead for ten thousand years.

128
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,599
The seal he left behind

129
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,039
has grown weaker and weaker.

130
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,439
And all this time,

131
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,159
as you grew stronger,

132
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,199
I made several moves

133
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,359
and reclaimed quite a bit of power.

134
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,799
I broke the seal long ago

135
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:13,639
and took back that portion of Heavenly Retribution power.

136
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,479
I have become the true

137
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,599
God of Destruction.

138
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,639
Then I pretended nothing had happened

139
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,959
and watched you all

140
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,879
fight desperately like clowns,

141
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:31,079
thinking you were close to victory,

142
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,639
only to fall straight into the abyss once more.

143
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,799
It was truly hilarious.

144
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,440
Also...

145
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,359
The moment I became the God of Heavenly Retribution,

146
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,119
the moment I became the God of Heavenly Retribution,

147
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,759
I cast away that lowly demonic beast of yours.

148
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,879
The blood pact between you and it

149
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:51,079
can no longer affect me.

150
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,479
And you even went through the trouble
of hiding it away,

151
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,879
planning to use it against me.

152
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,600
Brother.

153
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:03,680
Haochen...

154
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,159
You didn’t really think

155
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,319
this would be enough to stop me, did you?

156
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,039
Everything in this world

157
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,879
shall return to destruction

158
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,639
before the God of Heavenly Retribution.

159
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,999
Killing you three inferior gods

160
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,239
is no different to me

161
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:52,399
than crushing an ant.

162
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,000
Does this look familiar,

163
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,240
Feng Xiu?

164
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:05,639
This is

165
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:08,439
the very strike that once destroyed the Primordial Lands.

166
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:12,359
The scene from six thousand years ago
shall repeat itself.

167
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,799
When I return,

168
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:18,519
the entire world will fall into ruin.

169
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,079
Destruction

170
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,600
has arrived.

171
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,359
The defenses of Yulong Pass have been breached.

172
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:37,719
The Holy Demon Continent is in danger.

173
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:38,839
Haochen,

174
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,319
focus on dealing with the God of Heavenly Retribution.

175
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,840
Leave the rest to me.

176
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,919
I will protect the Holy Demon Continent for you

177
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,639
and safeguard everyone.

178
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,360
Cai’er,

179
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,479
protect yourself.

180
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,839
You too.

181
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:51,599
Don’t forget our promise.

182
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:01,919
One of them slipped away.

183
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,640
No matter.

184
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,999
In the end, they all have to die.

185
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:11,800
Feng Xiu,

186
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,399
you pathetic stray dog,

187
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,439
you actually dare face me directly?

188
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,639
You spent a thousand years

189
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:17,839
plotting your revenge,

190
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,039
thinking you could destroy the Holy Demon Continent

191
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,519
and thereby destroy me.

192
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:23,640
Who would’ve thought

193
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,399
you’d lose so miserably to Long Haochen?

194
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,999
A total defeat.

195
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:30,119
Even those two brothers of yours,
who didn’t leave a single bone behind,

196
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,679
died for your sake.

197
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,559
You’re still just as much of a failure as you were six thousand years ago.

198
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,999
No one can be protected.

199
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:42,119
They can only be killed by me.

200
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,919
You are the true culprit behind all of this.

201
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,600
You...

202
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,919
are not worthy of speaking any victim’s name.

203
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:58,800
Lingxuan...

204
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,400
This child

205
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,879
really does take after you.

206
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:05,800
Haochen,

207
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,080
in your current state,

208
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,079
you cannot defeat the God of Heavenly Retribution.

209
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,559
You must fully merge the power of both gods.

210
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:18,199
Grandpa...

211
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,640
What are you going to do?

212
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:29,399
Farewell,

213
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,400
my child.

214
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,239
No...

215
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,720
Grandpa!

216
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,119
I am the greatest Demon God Emperor

217
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,679
in the history of the Demon Race.

218
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:48,599
The supreme powerhouse unmatched in all of heaven and earth.

219
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:52,319
For six thousand years,

220
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,799
this towering hatred

221
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,479
has bathed my body day and night.

222
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,921
I must have my revenge,
then lead my people home.

223
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,279
Compared to this long journey,

224
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,599
a single year is as fleeting as morning dew.

225
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,919
Yet I have remembered it for so long...

226
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:09,880
so very long.

227
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,199
Perhaps because only during that one year

228
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,239
did I not have to be the Demon God Emperor.

229
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,999
I didn’t have to live solely for hatred.

230
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,439
I was simply Feng Ling.

231
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:26,520
Lingxuan...

232
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,600
After you left,

233
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,159
I began to learn your gentleness,

234
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,239
your compassion.

235
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,559
As if in doing so,

236
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:40,241
a part of you could continue living on within me.

237
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,519
Later,

238
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,519
everyone I cared about—

239
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,559
my flesh and blood,

240
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,199
my brothers—

241
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:50,319
all met the same fate as you.

242
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,679
I couldn’t protect a single one of them.

243
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,360
But in the end,

244
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,159
even if it costs me everything,

245
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,319
I will protect

246
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,639
our Haochen.

247
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:33,719
I will use my godhood,

248
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,320
my divine power,

249
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,239
to forge them into your Sword of Divinity.

250
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:42,880
Only then

251
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:46,559
will you be able to wield the full power of both gods.

252
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:49,560
Grandpa...

253
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:51,639
I already killed you once.

254
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,799
I shattered your heart.

255
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,840
Now...

256
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:58,159
I’m giving it back to you, Grandpa.

257
00:15:14,549 --> 00:15:31,839
[I’m sorry, Haochen… you were right. Everything the living beings of the Primordial Land suffered should never be repeated on the Sacred Demon Continent. Now, I entrust my will—along with the will of the former Primordial Land—to you.”]

258
00:15:34,141 --> 00:15:39,787
- Fall of the Gods -

259
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:54,119
I will carry out the will to protect,

260
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:57,159
bearing your will

261
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:00,479
and the will of two worlds,

262
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,999
to defeat the God of Heavenly Retribution.

263
00:16:05,280 --> 00:16:07,799
That old man really was good to you, huh?

264
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:11,279
He actually used a sacrifice like this

265
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:13,959
to grant you the power of two gods.

266
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:16,759
Austin Griffin...

267
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,759
The power of light and god-slaying,

268
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:23,239
the ultimate force of salvation in this world

269
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,519
and the ultimate force of slaughter.

270
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,159
When the two become one,

271
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,799
even a god who can destroy everything

272
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:35,519
should tremble before it.

273
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,799
The power of two gods...

274
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,679
Not bad at all.

275
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,279
This is the first time

276
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,359
since the birth of the universe

277
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:06,119
that anyone has managed to wound the God of Heavenly Retribution.

278
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:10,759
You are qualified to see this sword.

279
00:17:16,080 --> 00:17:17,199
This sword

280
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,239
is called Destruction.

281
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,239
